### First Party External Instrumentation Config - Node.js

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/documentation/module-instrumentations.md

Configuration for a first-party external instrumentation, identifying the npm package to be used for instrumentation. No 'type' is needed as the package identifier is sufficient.

```javascript
'koa': {module: '@newrelic/koa'}
```

